name: timtripcony.github.com
tagline: An overview of my GitHub repositories
body:
### [com.timtripcony.domino.collections](http://timtripcony.github.com/com.timtripcony.domino.collections/)
Convenience wrappers for Domino collection objects to make them behave more like the Java Collections API

### [org.openntf.xsp.extlib](https://github.com/timtripcony/org.openntf.xsp.extlib)
OSGi plugin that extends the XPages runtime portion of the IBM Domino platform
